Usage: highlight [-help] [<object>+] [-index <integer>] [ -color <string> | -auto_color  | -original  ] [ -pattern <string> | -original  ]

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
<object>+                 # Specifies Object Pointer List.
                          # ((any_object)+, optional)
-auto_color               # Specifies Object color automatically.
                          # (bool, optional)
-color <string>           # Specifies the color value for the specified object.
                          # (string, optional)
-index <integer>          # Specifies the index value for the specified object.
                          # (int, optional, min=1, max=256)
-original                 # Highlight the object through original color.
                          # (bool, optional)
-pattern <string>         # Specifies the pattern value for the specified
                          # object. (string, optional)